      <title>沙烏地阿拉伯上調油價後油價小幅走高</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-nudges-higher-after-saudi-arabia-hikes-prices-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙烏地阿拉伯上調大部分地區 6 月原油價格後，週一石油期貨小幅上漲，加薩停火協議的前景似乎渺茫，再次引發人們對以色列與哈馬斯衝突可能在這個主要產油地區擴大的擔憂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-nudges-higher-after-saudi-arabia-hikes-prices-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 01:48:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
